wiki.summary: On “Wizard Of Oz,” Logic boasts about how far he got in his career, and compares himself to The Wizard of Oz, who is is known to be the only man in the kingdom who can solve anyone’s problem. Similarly, Logic claim he’s running the rap game and helping his fans with his songs. The song was first teased on Logic’s Instagram in January of 2018. Read more on Last.fm.
